' ===================================================================
' CROSS-CONTEXT RELATIONSHIPS
' ===================================================================
DashboardShellView ..> ProcurementStore : reads PO data
DashboardShellView ..> RequisitionStore : reads requisitions
DashboardShellView ..> InventoryStore : reads inventory
DashboardShellView ..> SuppliersStore : reads suppliers
DashboardShellView ..> AnalyticsStore : reads budgets

DeliveryTrackingView ..> DeliveryStore : manages deliveries
UsersManagementView ..> IamStore : manages users

LayoutComponent ..> IamStore : reads session

@enduml
